==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One minute blue, and the next minute white.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī zhèn qīng yī zhèn bái

===Idiom===
'''[[一阵]][[青]][[一阵]][[白]]'''

# Describes the change someone's facial expression when they become surpirsed or angry.

===Alternate forms===
[[一陣青一陣白]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

